name: curl
desc:
The cURL package contains an utility and a library used for 
transferring files with URL syntax to any of the following protocols: 
FTP, FTPS, HTTP, HTTPS, SCP, SFTP, TFTP, TELNET, DICT, LDAP, LDAPS 
and FILE. Its ability to both download and upload files can be 
incorporated into other programs to support functions 
like streaming media.
